CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, February 24, 1945, pg. 17, reads: "BIG FIVE BASKETEERS - This is a shot of the Centre Avenue YMCA Big Five cage team, slated to clash with the Belle Vernon Rens this Friday at the Centre Avenue YMCA, at 8:30 P.M. Left to right: Andrew Ford, Richard Britton, Robert Coles, Frank Enty, George Hogan, James Lipscombe, Clarence Johnson, captain, and Harold Warren. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Group portrait of Centre Avenue YMCA basketball team, from left: Andrew Ford, Richard Britton, Robert Coles, Frank Enty, George Hogan, James Lipscombe, captain Clarence Johnson, and Harold Warren, posed in gymnasium
